In order to run properly You need to do the following things:

1. Install XAMPP
2. Down repository to XAMPP/htdocs/studies-weekly
3. Create a database named "education"
4. create a table called "articles"
5. Create a table with the following fields and types:
    id int (Primary Key and Auto Increment)
    articleTitle text
    articleBody text
    articleAuthor text
    articaleDate date
6. You will now be able to run the program by going to https://localhost/studies-weekly